{
  "texts": [
    "To successfully embrace and deploy the I5.0 concept in the industry, all stakeholders should invest and collaborate in creating solutions that are a compelling fusion of technology and perceived values, moving away from sole digitalization toward long-term human service [35].At the dawn of industrial revolutions, the scarcity of practical solutions or prototypes to guide factories in integrating and adapting innovative concepts to their environment slowed down the new revolution in the industry.",
    "Small-to medium-sized factories are the most vulnerable because they need proper internal resources and structures to adopt new plant technologies [36].",
    "Therefore, there is a crucial need for more research and work that creates practical solutions for factories adapted to different working conditions in relation to the upcoming industrial revolution.",
    "Regarding the new I5.0, solutions built for factories need to consider a combination of advanced technological concepts (like in I4.0) while prioritizing humans and the planet's well-being.",
    "Generative pre-training transformer (GPT) modelsThe generative pre-training transformer (GPT) [37] is a large generative language model invented by OpenAI, combining several AI models for diverse language generation tasks.GPT achieves outstanding performance in various natural language activities, with results very similar to human-like natural conversations, prompts, and queries, partly thanks to the generous amount of its pre-trained dataset and its transformer decoder deep learning architecture utilized for feature extraction [37,38].The GPT technology became popular in November 2022 with the official launch of the notable chatbot ChatGPT by OpenAI."
  ]
}